Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明野美星 修学旅行回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色友人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}以下皆为北海道著名特产·伪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八花亭的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木制人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙挂件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是这个我特意带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 吸 呼 吸试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道的清香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 回去当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就按计划那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是 身体没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在11点的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在站前广场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧 干嘛要问我啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天好像是放假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在白天？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得可疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 他们也认识那么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 小夜学姐也一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准备要去哪啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我倒不觉得...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说下 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我可是为了大八木你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被江户川君叫过来的 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话先说好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买书路过的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路过路过路过 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分百在约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 有事会发生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我也该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样都要坚持到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在到哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部 部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江学姐！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去去去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也超在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小点声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此 昨天就该问下部长的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 现在这边要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 觉得的还是草间老师最理解她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小夜学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车站附近取照片的时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得很可疑就跟过来了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 你们在想什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是这样组合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 我多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 只是路过这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用高跟鞋走这路太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 今年也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候在的 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先说的话就一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他 怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在从观测会回来的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是差不多这样的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着今年也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母好像很忙 没法抽身过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是一个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 让你们吃了一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过爸爸肯定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到小朔 还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得他有一双很大的手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常开些不知是真是假的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常和美星 有时也和我一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也最喜欢美星了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直看着天空的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为即使我离开这小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小镇也永远不会变 永远都是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个小镇中消失的就只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的就保持这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家肯定在这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 小美星说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年和朔君看到流星了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 天全黑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星 到我家来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也会是个好天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的模考太真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还是第一次在校外考呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是近江介绍的一个预备校的模考
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江姐姐旁边的是哪个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是应试战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 快看快看 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天部长从近江同学那拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星凌日的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}最近一次是06年11月9号早上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 我们也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...你们在...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 今天要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法 大家还在想昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是想避开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又不知如何面对她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美一直像这样笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我所能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请各位回到教室后再做讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果开会到这么晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过的这呆掉的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是前天那时交给他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才过了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得已经错过最佳时机了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送书签做礼物的话 不会被误解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给男生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就这样等到天亮的话 会更难送出去的」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里读到过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽早送出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个纪念品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其它任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部这边好像很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君和美星学姐 突然陷入热恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 我现在很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.58,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 美星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 我们回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧 看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他凝视着美星学姐的时候那疲倦的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没出现过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 更没法交给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是今天还没法给他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为委员会的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能占用你一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 眼镜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家就有备用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉成与和泉都回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我就这样回去行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是校长像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样子被看见了 明野会不会误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟美星她们一个小学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要经过住宅区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也在住宅区那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美星同一个公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 还在啊 伊藤商店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这里变公寓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这玩具好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 忍不住就...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我啥都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到这个小镇以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没怎么重温过以前的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 没能更早点到这来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 之前会离开这个小镇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好眼镜坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从北海道带回来的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是文化祭的谢礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也有很多不明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的话来找我商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看到他现在的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是啪破君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么了 眼镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 之后的让我们来送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找你商量一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 今天也没来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之间考试的时候大家还一起复习来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直没说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能让他明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让人担心应该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出元气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然有几个限制条例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是同意你们使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这次 下不为例
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经好好做过调查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也问了其它学校的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以确定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是搞不清 天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我自己来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想帮忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真努力啊 明野一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样的话就好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到最近才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那么爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定无意中让她伤心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美她却...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实却几乎没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在电话里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概也只剩这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个大呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做些什么就不能平复的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们也来参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜学姐 部长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家 怎么办怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都别说 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文文 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是流星雨的团体观测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可要一起好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为考试忘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是双子座流星雨的极大日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家偷偷准备的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我只能做到这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是怕天气不好让你失望嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这些还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥你身为大龄学姐居然能哭得这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看 可以缩在被炉里边吃橘子边看星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为了我办了观测会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想一起看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星 有很多流星划过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望美星能和大家一起看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21分30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北河三的方向二等级
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个场面真梦幻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常听小朔说起爸爸说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到小朔现在心里还有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不是故意要瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把手牵起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的天空是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气晴朗 很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.29,0:22:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的力量 这就是爱的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.71,0:22:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才就想说了 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人没在交往啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:46.05,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫追星社
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:48.67,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 像那白雪一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:49.51,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
